                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wharton</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Egan</persName>.</hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-09-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 7, 1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Wharton asks whether Mr. Egan has received his telegram, of the 4th instant,
                    and directs him to telegraph his answer.</p>
            </div>
